    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready to go. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s looking for a new home where it can keep making memories. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat! Let's get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
