    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band and exceptional throttle response. Power is routed through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a factory limited-slip differential. This example has undergone a recent valve clearance adjustment and a thorough inspection of the rear subframe reinforcement points to ensure structural integrity. The chassis retains its signature balance with responsive MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with a well-loved performance vehicle, the mechanical vitals remain robust, offering a pure analog connection to the tarmac.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Reliable engine. Clean interior. Recent maintenance performed. Title in hand.",
      "price": 29500.0,
