    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that\u2019s been well-loved! It drives great, looks sharp, and is totally ready to hit the road with its next owner. I\u2019ve priced it to sell quickly, so come take a look and see for yourself how great it is!",
      "price": 28900.0,
