    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver-focused example is mechanically sound, boasting a recently overhauled VANOS unit and reinforced rear subframe mounting points to ensure chassis rigidity. The limited-slip differential provides excellent traction coming out of corners, while the suspension maintains its original damping characteristics with updated bushings. Though it shows minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the engine pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline with perfect compression across all cylinders. A mechanically honest M-car for the serious enthusiast.",
